ected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,40],"id":"dd970e25-e267-10de-0b2e-ec9e3499d4ee","name":"Note: Notify Assigned Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warm → Drip via Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"8dae7249-87e1-52ae-3273-da6f382c1932","name":"Note: Warm → Drip via Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cold → Park in Nurture List\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,1000],"id":"8efddf9f-1418-c0c9-3b71-df1236d8bc9e","name":"Note: Cold → Park in Nurture List"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Combine Lead Paths\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"8708fed6-f78e-706b-5e24-48b8bb5d36ee","name":"Note: Combine Lead Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"1709d4b4-3900-ce8b-fe60-0607bfc893bf","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"a75a7526-68f3-e80f-8048-3ec0d2bdeb6a","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"8b5c67ac-3781-01d4-1236-b89709cecdf2","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"61dd5248-37c4-1691-b052-8e496702d47b","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"0039c8b7-6730-8a7c-6972-b3a3b127ff2b","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"0becc3a5-aef5-a92c-1b3b-31032b4dd98f","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per email (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"79241aa3-c0e2-95b2-cafe-93ea29834e47","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"8f3d2d89-2503-405c-412f-687e9711e8ae","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"4727f0e9-b251-45fe-76e8-35369771cb38","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"a31514b4-0bab-885f-11c6-e9e8a85c41a7","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"6beccd58-0ee3-a42a-4749-403742423aa2","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"c10e1517-ee6a-f88a-73c3-7c1070f74255","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"9067ee8a-391c-9fef-9906-bb286767caf4","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9066,520],"id":"5585ee4b-eef9-9c1a-cd2c-f79b3c9ea405","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9390,520],"id":"32dab72c-07e6-4b19-1233-2402aa12e572","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9714,520],"id":"94d923ff-6377-7c78-2eb0-2e64af33b079","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10038,520],"id":"ba7428c5-bdf1-913c-dbb2-7a5f2d33fffe","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10362,520],"id":"22ed3d36-32ec-82f5-6baf-d3e26b3ed3ad","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9714,1540],"id":"cf6f0389-6bbc-4e59-d58f-bcbef0087b6a","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10038,1540],"id":"ddb1baf5-7b58-59e1-392d-847edae2016d","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10362,1540],"id":"1fa3258b-899e-012a-f35e-fffd330ddebe","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Nurture trial users with Airtable and Outlook on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** Drip Sequence · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nNurture trial users with Airtable and Outlook on autopilot. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual auto-responders is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Normalize Email Payload → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → Notion + Instant Ping → Notify Assigned Owner → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to drip sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating auto-responders in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Improves response time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"386e5cf1-e3f1-378f-db7e-a81b41ccf011","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"5d5d5bfa-5af9-6e56-3053-aacb6644495b","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"a28343f8-7523-1ec4-2e6f-932f8ff6ca2d","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your auto-responders process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"73518ea5-5a46-2135-f495-8ba15ab49ccf","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Email Payload","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Email Payload":{"main":[[{"node":"Score the Lead","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score the Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Assign Round-Robin Owner","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Assign Round-Robin Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Heat","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot → Notion + Instant Ping":{"main":[[{"node":"Notify Assigned Owner","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Heat":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot → Notion + Instant Ping","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warm → Drip via Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Cold → Park in Nurture List","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Notify Assigned Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warm → Drip via Outlook":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cold → Park in Nurture List":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Combine Lead Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"31bb5b2a-0379-4441-aeae-aaa2e31c99ba","id":"FDX02979"}